<p>This web page describes resources, related to Bulgarian projects for creating, supporting and improving free software and documentation. In general, these projects are efforts of the whole <A href="http://fsa-bg.org/bin/view.cgi/Fsasite/WebHomeEn">Bulgarian free software community</A> to translate and adopt free software and documentation in Bulgarian language. If you wish to help us, please don't hesitate to contact with the relevant coordinators. For instance, if you wish to contribute to <A href="http://www.debian.org/">Debian</A>, but you have no programming skills, you can still help with translating <A href="http://www.bg.debian.org/devel/website/translating">Debian web pages</A> in your natural language. If you have good knowledge (technical is not necessary, but useful) of English language and wish to see these pages in Bulgarian, please contact with the coordinator of Debian Bulgarian Translation Project - <a href="mailto:rkrastev@obs.bg">Rumen Krasstev</a>.
</p>

<p><em>Many of listed projects below are contributed and supported by members of</em> <a href="http://fsa-bg.org/bin/view.cgi/Fsasite/WebHomeEn"><strong>"Free Software Association - Bulgaria"</strong></a>.
</p>

<p>Debian specific resources:
</p>
<UL>
<LI><strong>Debian book in Bulgarian</strong> -
       <a href="ftp://ftp.uni-sofia.bg/debian-book/index.html">ftp://ftp.uni-sofia.bg/debian-book/index.html</a>. 
<LI>Debian Bulgarian users mailing list (recommended encoding - utf8 or cp1251) - 
       <a href="http://debian.gabrovo.com/mailing.php">debian-bg@lists.gabrovo.com</a>. Supported by the "Debian for Bulgarians" <a href="http://debian.gabrovo.com/">web site</a>. 
</UL>  

<p>Resources for translators: 
</p>
<UL>
  <LI>Most important mailing list for discussions and information of free software and documentation translations in Bulgarian language - <a href="http://debian.fmi.uni-sofia.bg/mailman/listinfo/ls-dict">LS-Dict mailing list</a>.
  <LI>Very useful information for translators - dictionaries, mailing lists, etc:
       <a href="http://fsa-bg.org/bin/view.cgi/Fsasite/InfoTranslators">Translating free software in Bulgarian language</a>.
</UL>

<p>Other Bulgarian translation projects of free software and documentation:
</p>
<UL>
  <LI><a href="http://gnome.cult.bg">Gnome Bulgarian Translation Project</a>.
  <LI><a href="http://fsa-bg.org/bin/view.cgi/Fsasite/KdePage">KDE Bulgarian Translation Project</a>.
 <LI><a href="http://bgoffice.sourceforge.net">BG Office Project</a>. Spell checker, thesaurus, hyphenation and other tools for OpenOffice, aspell, ispell, Mozilla and others.
</UL>

<p>General Linux specific resources:
