<LI>Linux Bulgarian users mailing list (recommended encoding - utf8):
       <a href="http://www.linux-bulgaria.org/public/mail_list.html">lug-bg@linux-bulgaria.org</a>. Supported by the "Linux-Bulgaria.org" <a href="http://debian.gabrovo.com/">web site</a>.   
